entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#0
entry.value: All xenos and traitors are blights, to be cleansed from the galaxy.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#1
entry.value: At the Lord Commander's order.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#2
entry.value: Death at our hands is no dishonour.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#3
entry.value: In the Emperor's name.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#4
entry.value: My fist, clenched tight in ceramite, smashes with the force of a Chapter.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#5
entry.value: So fall all enemies of the Imperium.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#6
entry.value: Through the destruction of our enemies do we earn our salvation.

entry.name: SpaceMarines/TacticalSpaceMarine:Victory#7
entry.value: We are the Emperor's vengeance, made flesh.
